										<h1 class="pagetitle">In Graphic Detail: Pirates on the Horizon</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">A surge in piracy threatens to upend positive trends in maritime safety.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/jess-craig/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Jess Craig</a>								<br/>
